ctic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.mkEqMPR","doc":"Construct the `Expr` `h.mpr e`, from a `Simp.Result` with proof `h`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.mkEqMPR\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkEqMPR</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L551-L553","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.mkCast","line":551,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.mkCast","doc":"Construct the `Expr` `cast h e`, from a `Simp.Result` with proof `h`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.mkCast\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkCast</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class