lass=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dandThen</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f </span><span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">DSimproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">DSimproc</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L372-L373","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc","line":372,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instAndThenSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#AndThen\">AndThen</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Simproc</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L357-L370","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen","line":357,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen","doc":"\"Compose\" the two given simplification procedures. We use the following semantics.\n- If `f` produces `done` or `visit`, then return `f`'s result.\n- If `f` produces `continue`, then apply `g` to new expression returned by `f`.\n\nSee `Simp.Step` type.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">andThen</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f </span><span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Simproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Simproc</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L350-L355","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","line":350,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkEqTransResultStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L343-L348","name":"Lean.TransformStep.toStep","line":343,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">toStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Transform.html#Lean.TransformStep\">TransformStep</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L338-L341","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","line":338,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","doc":"Similar to `Simproc`, but resulting expression should be definitionally equal to the input one.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L336-L336","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","line":336,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L330-L334","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","line":330,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","doc":"A simplification procedure. Recall that we have `pre` and `post` procedures.\nSee `Step`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L328-L328","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","line":328,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L321-L327","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","line":321,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","doc":"For `pre` procedures, continue transformation by visiting subexpressions, and then\nexecuting `post` procedures.\n\nFor `post` procedures, this is equivalent to returning `visit`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">continue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L314-L320","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","line":314,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","doc":"For `pre` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again.\n\nFor `post` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again IF\n`Simp.Config.singlePass := false` and resulting expression is not equal to initial expression.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">visit</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L308-L313","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","line":308,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","doc":"For `pre` procedures, it returns the result without visiting any subexpressions.\n\nFor `post` procedures, it returns the result.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">done</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L304-L328","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step","line":304,"kind":"inductive","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step","doc":"Result type for a simplification procedure. We have `pre` and `post` simplification procedures.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L300-L302","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.modifyDiag","line":300,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.modifyDiag","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.modifyDiag\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">modifyDiag</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Diagnostics\">Diagnostics</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Diagnostics\">Diagnostics</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L297-L298","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.dsimp","line":297,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.dsimp","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.dsimp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dsimp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L294-L295","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.simp","line":294,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.simp","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.simp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">simp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Ta